<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbc1ed0b2-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s2323"><num value="2323">§ 2323.</num><heading> Basis of appraisal</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Except for lots sold pursuant to the provisions of <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s2347/a">section 2347(a) of this title</ref>, the appraised value shall be the current fair market value of the Government’s interest in the property.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbc1ed0b3-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/act/1955-08-04/ch543">Aug. 4, 1955, ch. 543</ref>, ch. 3, § 33, <ref href="/us/stat/69/474">69 Stat. 474</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
